{"tid":1738154,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"點解成個熱門無人講尖東同彌敦道攬炒成果","createTime":"2019-11-19T07:05:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T03:13:32.000Z","uid":273218,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9acccdcd91a2e84c560f0e894da539d2888d56cd","tid":1738154,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:05:15.000Z","msg":"講真，彌敦道自上星期已取消左好多巴士線<br />\n條路又搞成咁我都好幾日無入去<br />\n呢幾日大圍捕黑警封晒成個九龍半島<br />\n基本上商戶肯定少好多生意<br />\n再咁樣圍poly其實佢地都好大壓力<br />\n有無巴打絲打報下攬炒情況振奮下軍心<br />\n如果今晚或聽晚和理非再進場百周年公園有無得諗<br />\n記住攬炒係大家好多人目標及共識<br />\n只要商舖同公共交通收皮<br />\n大家可以流水式撤退不應戀戰打狗"},{"pid":"8a4c2fa28028990afbf325ba6fa6a45734c59682","tid":1738154,"uid":273991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:06:20.000Z","msg":"我公司係尖咀既餐廳<br />\n已經一個星期冇開喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蝕到hihi"},{"pid":"27056d1b51301bf8071f0cb2c8b4116e365711ec","tid":1738154,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:06:43.000Z","msg":"認同請幫推"},{"pid":"ed0265f7c656bf67f1e8b88380fd80c6c8b21973","tid":1738154,"uid":273218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8a4c2fa28028990afbf325ba6fa6a45734c59682","tid":1738154,"uid":273991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:06:20.000Z","msg":"我公司係尖咀既餐廳<br />\n已經一個星期冇開喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蝕到hihi"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:07:41.000Z","msg":"好似有人想冷處理攬炒，然後無限引戰引手足被捕<br />\n其實等和理非進場先出去<br />\n然後10點前撤退<br />\n會安全好多"},{"pid":"43aa95af2bcb67e161d3c073dd35a96ac0720e91","tid":1738154,"uid":47149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:12:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4ba512359cc1093d43edb9bc0385b7a638b964","tid":1738